---
// About Section - Sobre a empresa
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <!-- Header da Seção -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-on-scroll fade-up">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-black mb-6">
        Por que escolher a 
        <span class="text-[#00bc61] relative">
          Prado
          <svg class="absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-full h-3" viewBox="0 0 200 12" fill="none">
            <path d="M2 10C20 5 40 2 60 3C80 4 100 7 120 4C140 1 160 5 180 8C185 9 190 10 198 10" stroke="#00bc61" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" class="animate-pulse"/>
          </svg>
        </span>?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-[#A7A9AC] max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Somos uma empresa jovem e inovadora, focada em entregar soluções digitais 
        que realmente fazem a diferença no seu negócio.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-16">
      
      <!-- Conteúdo Principal -->
      <div class="animate-on-scroll fade-left">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-6">
          Nossa Missão
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-[#A7A9AC] mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Democratizar o acesso à tecnologia de qualidade, criando soluções digitais 
          acessíveis e eficientes que impulsionam o crescimento de empresas e profissionais.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Diferenciais -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 group">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-[#00bc61]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#00bc61]/20 transition-colors duration-300">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#00bc61]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black mb-2">Foco na Inovação</h4>
              <p class="text-[#A7A9AC]">Utilizamos as tecnologias mais atuais do mercado para criar soluções modernas e eficientes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 group">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-[#00bc61]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#00bc61]/20 transition-colors duration-300">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#00bc61]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black mb-2">Atendimento Personalizado</h4>
              <p class="text-[#A7A9AC]">Cada cliente é único. Oferecemos atenção personalizada e soluções sob medida para suas necessidades.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 group">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-[#00bc61]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#00bc61]/20 transition-colors duration-300">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#00bc61]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black mb-2">Crescimento Conjunto</h4>
              <p class="text-[#A7A9AC]">Seu sucesso é o nosso sucesso. Criamos parcerias duradouras e acompanhamos seu crescimento.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Visual -->
      <div class="relative animate-on-scroll fade-right">
     
        <!-- Grid de Cards -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <!-- Card Qualidade -->
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:border-[#00bc61]/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 group">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#00bc61] to-[#00a555] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h5 class="font-bold text-black mb-2 text-lg">Qualidade</h5>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#A7A9AC] leading-relaxed">Código limpo e bem estruturado</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Card Agilidade -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:border-[#00bc61]/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 group">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#00bc61] to-[#00a555] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h5 class="font-bold text-black mb-2 text-lg">Agilidade</h5>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#A7A9AC] leading-relaxed">Desenvolvimento rápido e eficiente</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Card Suporte -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:border-[#00bc61]/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 group">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#00bc61] to-[#00a555] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192L5.636 18.364M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5 0a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h5 class="font-bold text-black mb-2 text-lg">Suporte</h5>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#A7A9AC] leading-relaxed">Sempre disponível quando precisar</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Card Tecnologia -->
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:border-[#00bc61]/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 group">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#00bc61] to-[#00a555] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h5 class="font-bold text-black mb-2 text-lg">Tecnologia</h5>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#A7A9AC] leading-relaxed">Stack moderno e atualizado</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <div class="mt-16 text-center animate-on-scroll fade-up animation-delay-400">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-4">
          Pronto para começar seu projeto?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-[#A7A9AC] mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Vamos conversar sobre suas necessidades e criar uma solução digital 
          que impulsione seu negócio para o próximo nível.
        </p>
        <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-[#00bc61] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#00a555] hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[#00bc61]/25 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 group">
          <span>Vamos conversar</span>
          <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Animações baseadas em scroll - otimizadas para mobile */
  .animate-on-scroll {
    opacity: 0;
    transition: all 0.4s ease-out;
  }
  
  .animate-on-scroll.fade-up {
    transform: translateY(15px);
  }
  
  .animate-on-scroll.fade-left {
    transform: translateX(-15px);
  }
  
  .animate-on-scroll.fade-right {
    transform: translateX(15px);
  }
  
  .animate-on-scroll.animate-in {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translate(0, 0);
  }
  
  .animation-delay-400 {
    transition-delay: 0.1s;
  }
  
  /* Mobile: animações mais rápidas e sem delays */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .animate-on-scroll {
      transition: all 0.3s ease-out;
    }
    
    .animation-delay-400 {
      transition-delay: 0s !important;
    }
    
    .animate-on-scroll.fade-up,
    .animate-on-scroll.fade-left,
    .animate-on-scroll.fade-right {
      transform: translateY(10px);
    }
  }
</style> 